RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 1 6F Dirt CR: 25. Claiming Purse 6664. FOR NATIVE THREE YEAR OLDS. Weight, 118 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since February 24 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since January 24 Allowed 2 lbs. Claiming Price $8,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: CENTRALINO led throughout, prevailed. GALATEO CENTRO pressed pace, gamely. LUCKY APOLLO off pace, best of rest. CONTROVERSIAL weakened. VIENTO VELOZ dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 2 6F Dirt CR: 70. Allowance Purse 10780. FOR NATIVE FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since March 9 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since February 24 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since January 24 Allowed 4 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: LATIN MAMBO pressed pace, led, prevailed. ESTRELLA DE BELEN late kick outside. DERRUMBE close up, evenly. GASTRICA set pace, gave way. DONA MONIN trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 3 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 54. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since March 9 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since February 24 Allowed 3 lbs. A Ra ce Since January 24 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: MILA stalked pace, led, driving. COLONY DREAMER late kick. GET SMARTER set pace, drew clear, weakened. LA EDUCADORA loomed, wide turn. QUERELLA off pace, improved position. ABSOLUT MERICAN close up, weakened. LA ECUACION failed to menace. QUEEN KRISTAL dropped back. WIRE ON FIRE failed to menace. COMPETITIVE STAR dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 4 6F Dirt CR: 67. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE SINCE MARCH 24 AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. 5# A clasf.$4,000 y debts Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: POKERIST chased, led, driving. BACANO off slowly, finished well outside. ALYCAR FLASH loomed, flattened out. RELENTLESS LION off pace, 7 wide, finished well. SMALL TOWN SHUFFLE vied for lead, weakened. CARAMELO failed to menace. MY UNCLE TITAN off slowly, no menace. NO BRASS NO AMMO dropped back. CHITUZZE seated rider start, dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 5 6F Dirt CR: 66. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE SINCE MARCH 24 AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. 5# A clasf.$4,000 y debts Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: ROARING THUNDER pressed pace, led, driving. DRAKES'S FORTUNE off pace, gaining. TELL HIM vied for lead inside, grudgingly. RAISE THE ANCHOR best of rest. TAPITOR gamely fourth. MASTEROFTHEHOUSE gamely fourth. RUN HAPPY STAR off slowly, improved position. GEOSCIENCE vied for lead, dropped back. VALID STORM dropped back. LAND BATTLE failed to menace.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 6 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 49. Maiden Special Weight Purse 11000. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 120 lbs.; Older, 123 lbs. 4# A clasf. inferior y debts Allowed 4 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: GLORY AND VICTORY led, drew off. GOLDEN CT outside, finished well for place. TACTICAL STRIDE vied for lead, gave way. EL ZAFIRO pressed pace, brushed late. TWO PARTNERS improved position. DOUBLETON weakened. DR. RICKY A. failed to menace. KEEN CAUSEWAY dropped back. WOODVILLE'S MUSIC inside, dropped back. DON DANY R. off slowly, no menace.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 7 1M Dirt CR: 82. Claiming Purse 6500. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON THREE RACES SINCE MARCH 24 AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $14,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since March 9 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since February 24 Allowed 3 lbs. A RaceS ince January 24 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $8,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: PLATO outside, driving. MURAT close up, bid, led, second best. LOVE IN PARADISE off pace, finished well. SOLD OUT bid, flattened out. UP THE MOON off pace, some gain. UNCLE GREGORY chased, weakened. RUN ON THE TRAIL set pace, weakened. REDOUX dropped back. TOUPHA failed to menace.
